s of music turned out to be highly danceable.\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 1120, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 913, \"end\": 917, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Herc\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.919550371157468e-33, \"text\": \"Herc\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Herc\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Herc\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most danceable parts\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 953}, {\"ngram\": \"songs\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 962}, {\"ngram\": \"the same record\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1010}, {\"ngram\": \"two turntables\", \"from\": 1014, \"to\": 1028}, {\"ngram\": \"the sample\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1053}, {\"ngram\": \"those long stretches\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1076}, {\"ngram\": \"music\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1085}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For decades, many media outlets have referred to the dance form as \\\"breakdancing,\\\" but several practitioners interviewed for this article said they prefer the term \\\"breaking.\\\"\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1297, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"decades\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1133}, {\"ngram\": \"many media outlets\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1153}, {\"ngram\": \"the dance form\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1185}, {\"ngram\": \"several practitioners\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1230}, {\"ngram\": \"this article\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1259}, {\"ngram\": \"the term\", \"from\": 1277, \"to\": 1285}]}, {\"sentence\": \"John \\\"Flonetik\\\" Vinuya at a cypher in a \\\"down rock.\\\"\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1351, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"John \\\"Flonetik\\\" Vinuya\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1321}, {\"ngram\": \"a cypher\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1333}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"down rock\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1349}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Odylle 'Mantis' Beder is a veteran breaker who now performs with the crew Full Circle Souljahs and runs theBgirl Herstoryproject, which document